data.description: This home is the cleanest and the most eye appealing. Across from a luscious community park and perfect for running and getting your workout on. Ample parking and even room for the side by side. Ask for a tour all your own. Artificial turf front and even a porch for a rocking chair and table. Enjoy coffee while the kids are at the park. Security door offers the best of privacy and open air during the cool AZ nights fall has to offer. Do you work from home? Ideal office/den facing the outside is just what the relaxation gods ordered. Write your memoir or read the next chapter of your favorite book. The great room separates two ample bedrooms from the primary room. It's just all too perfect and guest what? The appliances convey. The size of the lot leaves space for new pool or sports court.
